abstract: Arizona Diamondbacks acquire pitching prospect Sam McWilliams from Philadelphia Phillies for pitcher Jeremy Hellickson.
lead_paragraph: The Arizona Diamondbacks traded the right-handed pitcher Jeremy Hellickson to the Philadelphia Phillies for the right-handed pitching prospect Sam McWilliams.
snippet: The Arizona Diamondbacks traded the right-handed pitcher Jeremy Hellickson to the Philadelphia Phillies for the right-handed pitching prospect Sam McWilliams.
